%TAG !u! tag:unity3d.com,2011:
--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 364c2b772391e46dba637935c558b9b2, type: 3}
  m_Name: Cave
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::MythSO
  pageNumber: 167
  mythName: Cave
  omens:
  - '1. A wide cave mouth looms from a vine-

    cloaked cliff. It seems empty,
    but echoes

    sound slightly altered.'
  - '2. Three iron pilgrims attempt to seal the

    cave, claiming it can only cause
    harm.'
  - '3. The Cave, a familiar shape and echo. This

    time a glow emanates from
    within,

    revealing 3 useful crystals (see opposite).'
  - '4. The Cave appears again, on a new cliff

    face, the word "gold" echos from
    within.

    Anybody entering awakens the beast of

    solid darkness, which
    only fights to

    prevent entry to the Cave. Beyond the

    beast lies a heavy
    coffer of gold.'
  - '5. The Cave appears on a great boulder, now

    with eye-like holes and tooth-like

    stalactites.
    It slowly speaks, granting one

    question to each Knight present. It knows

    all
    and answers to the best of its ability.'
  - '6. A towering figure strides out of a shadow,

    like folds of material darkness.
    He is the

    Debt Collector, here to take payment for

    the Cave. He accepts
    anything of value,

    and tries to kill those who won''t pay.'
  verse: 'A weary soul discerns no truth or lie

    An eager heart asks neither
    what or why'
  castEntries:
  - name: Beast of Solid Darkness
    statBlock: 'VIG 12, CLA 12, SPI 7, 8 GD

      A3 (darkness hardened to iron)'
    notes: 'Blade out of darkness (3d10)

      or burst of un-light (d8 blast)'
  - name: Iron Pilgrims, Lymon, Sid, Hayma
    statBlock: 'VIG 12, CLA 10, SPI 13, 3 GD

      Robes and chains, blacksmith
      tools'
    notes: 
  - name: Debt Collector, Ambralleon
    statBlock: 'VIG 16, CLA 16, SPI 7, 8 GD

      A2 (shadow form, cold plates)'
    notes: 'Black spear (2d8 hefty, can be thrown and

      called back into his
      hand). Can Smite.'
  flavorTable:
    title: USEFUL CRYSTALS
    columns:
    - header: Appearance
      values:
      - Flickering grey
      - Milky white
      - Dull ochre
      - Pale mauve
      - Swirling turquoise
      - Pulsing crimson
    - header: Power when Broken
      values:
      - d10 blast of lightning
      - Releases horrifying but harmless ghosts
      - Winter arrives immediately
      - Open up a flaming pit
      - (d10) in the ground Vision of a useful truth
      - Plants grow rapidly
  visibleByDefault: 0
  visibleMarkerPrefab: {fileID: 0}
